data.description: This charming move-in ready bungalow is located in prime Brunswick and upholds its original charm while still undergoing some recent upgrades. It has a total of 3 beds and 1 fully updated bath. Enter into the sun-drenched living room featuring freshly neutral painted walls and beautiful laminate flooring. Enjoy the spacious eat-in kitchen with ample cabinetry and room for a cozy dining space. Hidden behind the white sliding doors you will find a convenient laundry closet with shelving. Also placed on the first floor is the master suite and gorgeous full bath. Up the stairs are the additional 2 bedrooms featuring original built-ins, and newer windows. The spacious back deck is perfect for outdoor entertaining with seamless flow through the sliding doors. This home offers everything a new homeowner is looking for, schedule your private showing today!
